    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 22-85 years

          -  Diagnosis of Parkinson's disease

          -  Candidate for DBS

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Other significant neurological disorder

          -  Diagnosis of dementia

